item.description:
New weekly night dedicated to all genres within electronic music, from house to electro to trance. Will be a nice alternative to what is being offered on Wednesdays in Boston.

I will also be spinning at this event, along with friends Ju Lee and Kia Mazzi. I'll play mostly progressive house, trance and techno. Hope to see you guys there, we can talk and have some drinks together before my set. Come and show some support!
item.name: Hi Frequency Wednesdays @Venu
